oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Last Few Segments From a Plantation Party program ; Duke Of Paducah comedy routine
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various performances from the last few segments of a Plantation Party program. Performance of a comedy routine, performed by the Duke Of Paducah on the Plantation Party.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Duke Of Paducah
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (0:00) Charlie Lyon announces a Bugler tobacco advertisement / (1:25) Tom, Dick, and Harry perform a parody song about radio advertisements, possibly named "Radio Commercials Keep Me Broke" / (3:46) The Plantation Party cast perform "[Unidentified song]" / (4:50) Duke Of Paducah announces the closing statements with Charlie Lyon announcing a Bugler tobacco advertisement / (5:50) Charlie Lyon says goodnight to the audience / (6:01) Duke Of Paducah performs a comedy routine
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Duke of Paducah, 1901-1986; Plantation party (Radio program); Lyon, Charles, 1903-1985
